  "commit_message": "feat(diag): Add the 'cargo::default' group (#17033)\n\n### What does this PR try to resolve?\n\nAdds a \"visible by default\" lint group to mirror `clippy::all` which\nshould gain a `clippy::default` alias.\n\nPersonally, my motivation is to reduce noise in tests by making it easy\nto disable all lints except those under tests.\n\n### How to test and review this PR?",
